    isPlayer: 0
  - commentCount: 3
    s_comment:
    - text: You ended that entire sentence with a preposition; only a guilty thief
        would be so careless with their word order!
      extraData: ExtraData
      inputSetIndex: 1
      outputNodeIndex: -1
      outActionIndex: -1
      sprites: {fileID: 0}
      audios: {fileID: 0}
      visible: 1
    - text: You used 'it's' instead of 'its' in your written notes; your orthography
        is as messy as your suspicious alibi!
      extraData: ExtraData
      inputSetIndex: 1
      outputNodeIndex: -1
      outActionIndex: -1
      sprites: {fileID: 0}
      audios: {fileID: 0}
      visible: 1
    - text: You just used a 'redundancy' error by saying 'very big'; a true master
        of the dictionary would be more concise!
      extraData: ExtraData
      inputSetIndex: 1
      outputNodeIndex: 2
      outActionIndex: -1
      sprites: {fileID: 0}
      audios: {fileID: 0}
      visible: 1
    ID: 1
    pTag: Player
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
    vars: []
    varKeys: []
    isPlayer: 1
  - commentCount: 1
    s_comment:
    - text: Okay, okay! You caught me! My grammar failed me! I just wanted to pass
        the math exam so badly. Here is the calculator. I'm sorry!
      extraData: ExtraData
      inputSetIndex: 2
      outputNodeIndex: -1
      outActionIndex: -1
